   <refsynopsisdiv><title>Calling Sequence</title><synopsis>Output = curvature2d(Input)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
   
   <refsection><title>Description</title>
   
      <para>
 "curvature2d" calculates the curvature of an intensity  image or
 surface represented as a 2D matrix. It currently uses a simple finite
 difference scheme. </para>
   
   </refsection>
   
